title.rendered: EU Single Market Opportunities for Albanian SMEs

content.rendered:
The consultancy project, as financed by 𝐄𝐁𝐑𝐃 𝐒𝐌𝐄 𝐅&𝐃 𝐢𝐧 𝐀𝐥𝐛𝐚𝐧𝐢𝐚, aims to equip business community stakeholders, entrepreneurs, consultants and policymakers in Albania with the necessary knowledge and skills to navigate the complexities of the 𝐄𝐔 𝐒𝐢𝐧𝐠𝐥𝐞 𝐌𝐚𝐫𝐤𝐞𝐭 𝐏𝐫𝐨𝐠𝐫𝐚𝐦𝐦𝐞, its opportunities and enhance their competitiveness on the international stage.

In this respect, local SMEs require targeted support to enhance capacities and establish a better understanding on available opportunities and how to best utilise and benefit from EU funding calls and openings

@EBRD-Advice for Small Businesses in Albania
